{
  "texts": [
    "The GPT-4 generated scenario was merely designed to disguise the fact that participants were interacting with AI.",
    "Similar to the previous studies, both humans and GPT-4 were instructed to produce reappraisals that are two sentences long, to make sure that length did not impact the results.",
    "We also controlled for length in our analysis as in previous studies.",
    "Participants then rated the quality of reappraisal using the same four questions as in the previous studies (effectiveness, empathy, novelty, specificity).",
    "Finally, participants were asked whether they would be interested to continue the conversation with their counterpart."
  ]
}